<p>If you are accessing this site within the European Union please be aware that by providing East Lodge Capital with data: (i) you acknowledge and agree that due to the international operations of East Lodge Capital and its affiliates, East Lodge Capital may provide personal information, in accordance with its Privacy Policy, to East Lodge Capital’s affiliates that may be outside your resident jurisdiction, and that such data may be stored on servers located in other jurisdictions; and (ii) you consent to the transfer of such data outside of the European Union as described in the Privacy Policy. If you do not consent to the terms of the Privacy Policy, please do not use the Website, and, if you have provided personal identifying data, please contact East Lodge Capital about how you would like East Lodge Capital to handle such data.</p>
